query:
-- Create Riverside County agency if not exists
INSERT IGNORE INTO counties (name, state, usesStateProtocols, protocolVersion, createdAt)
VALUES ('Riverside County EMS Agency (REMSA)', 'California', 0, '2023', NOW());

-- Get the county ID
SET @riv_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Riverside%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- Insert Riverside County treatment protocols based on their numbering system (4xxx series)
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
-- Trauma protocols (4300 series)
(@riv_id, '4301', 'Shock Due to Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Shock Due to Trauma. Hemorrhage control, IV access, fluid resuscitation, and rapid transport to trauma center.', 'https://rivcoready.org/sites/g/files/aldnop181/files/2023-10/4301.pdf', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4302', 'Head Injury', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Head Injury. GCS assessment, airway management, and neuroprotective measures.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4303', 'Spinal Injury', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Spinal Injury. Spinal motion restriction, assessment, and transport considerations.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4304', 'Chest Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Chest Trauma. Assessment, needle decompression for tension pneumothorax, and chest seal application.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4305', 'Abdominal Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Abdominal Trauma. Assessment, evisceration management, and rapid transport.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4306', 'Extremity Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Extremity Trauma. Fracture management, splinting, and neurovascular assessment.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4307', 'Burns', 'Trauma', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Burns. Burn assessment, cooling, fluid resuscitation, and pain management.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),

-- Respiratory protocols (4400 series)
(@riv_id, '4401', 'Airway Management', 'Respiratory', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Airway Management. BLS and ALS airway techniques, including supraglottic airways and intubation.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4402', 'Asthma/COPD', 'Respiratory', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Asthma and COPD. Bronchodilator therapy, corticosteroids, and CPAP.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4403', 'Pulmonary Edema/CHF', 'Respiratory', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pulmonary Edema and CHF. CPAP, nitroglycerin, and diuretics.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4404', 'Respiratory Arrest', 'Respiratory', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Respiratory Arrest. Airway management and ventilation support.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4405', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Cardiac Arrest. CPR, defibrillation, and ACLS medications.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4406', 'Respiratory Distress', 'Respiratory', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Respiratory Distress. Assessment, oxygen therapy, and treatment based on etiology.', 'https://www.rivcoems.org/Portals/13/Documents/PolicyManual/2023/4406.pdf', '2023-01-01', 2023, NOW());
